    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to own! It's in great shape and has been really well-cared for, so it's totally ready to hit the road with you today. It runs super smoothly and is just perfect for someone who wants a reliable, quality ride without the brand-new price tag. I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so don't be shy\u2014let's get you in the driver's seat!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
