      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. The VANOS system has been meticulously maintained, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with road use, the mechanical vitals are robust, featuring a recently refreshed cooling system and bushings. A visceral, analog performance machine ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
