    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 represents a fantastic opportunity to own a luxury icon that has been treated with respect. Finished in a sophisticated Atomic Silver, the paint holds a brilliant luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a vehicle of this age. The interior is a sanctuary of Parchment leather; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All electronic amenities, including the heated/ventilated seats, navigation, and the premium audio system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history from certified technicians. The car recently passed a full inspection, featuring new brake pads and tires with approximately 75% tread remaining. This is a reliable, well-documented vehicle that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
